					<Image src="https://cdn.cosmicjs.com/c22dc300-4c7c-11f0-8d02-d7de9448d6b1-R5C_8279.jpg" pictureClass="col-span-12 sm:col-span-6 lg:col-span-3 lg:col-start-10" class="object-cover w-full h-full lg:object-right" sizes="30vw" />
				</div>
			</Container>

			<Container>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-y-8 md:gap-y-0">
					<h2 class="text-balance col-span-12 md:col-span-6">Where passion meets <span>decades of experience</span></h2>

					<div class="col-span-12 md:col-start-8 md:col-span-4 space-y-8">
						<Paragraph classes="text-stone-900 text-lg">
							Our team of experienced professionals brings over 80 years of combined expertise in restoring classic vehicles, and we are passionate about bringing these timeless off-road legends back to life with modern precision and
							craftsmanship.
						</Paragraph>

						<a href="/team" class="text-stone-950 text-lg font-bold">Meet Our Team &gt;</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</Container>

			<Container size="large">
				<div class="md:h-[40vh] md:min-h-[700px] grid grid-cols-12 md:grid-rows-2 gap-4 md:gap-6">
